platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: A comet has struck Mount Boom, and its up to you to assemble a quintet of adorable fiends to stave off a slimy slug invasion. Best Fiends is a unique take on the classic item-matching puzzler. Your team of canny critters will launch attacks, power up special abilities, and uncover hidden goodies across dozens of levels. From tricky obstacles to devastating special moves, theres plenty of strategy among the silliness.
